reviews.text: A small neighbourhood Chiu Chow style noodle joint. Noodles are reasonably priced for their portions. Meats and broth are not heavily flavoured by salt or MSG, which is good. BTW, the soup base of its beef noodle is rather unique (perhaps, from bonito?) so some may like it.

這間麵店我幫襯過幾次，食物其實ok. 牛腩，雲吞，韮菜餃都好吃。
飲品就算吧啦！
快快趣趣食一餐都算不錯的選擇。
Visited several times, the food is good, beef, dumpling are good.
Drink is so so. 
Good choice for a quick meal.
味道一般 牛雜未夠火候 菜太淋 飲品合格 三麵一菜兩凍飲一可樂 $133.
牛腩專家，中價，😋😆
用心經營! 十年來保持水準, 經濟抵食
